Welcome to InLook!

InLook is a fast, safe viewer for .eml email files. It opens a message in a
clean native window and shows its headers, body, and attachments — without
loading remote trackers or running anything the email tries to sneak in.

You're reading the plain-text version of this message, shown by clients that
don't render HTML.

Enjoy,
The InLook viewer

--inner
Content-Type: text/html; charset=utf-8
