<html><body>
<h2 style="color:#2c5282">Welcome to InLook 👋</h2>
<p>InLook is a <strong>fast, safe</strong> viewer for <code>.eml</code> email
files. If you can read this nicely formatted message, everything is working.</p>
<p>Here's what you're looking at:</p>
<ul>
  <li>The <strong>headers</strong> (From, To, Subject, Date) appear at the top</li>
  <li>The <strong>body</strong> renders inside a sandboxed iframe — no scripts,
      no network, no tracking</li>
  <li>Any <strong>attachments</strong> are listed below</li>
</ul>
<p>Remote content is blocked by default. The image below will
<em>not</em> load — that's on purpose, so hidden tracking pixels can't phone
home:</p>
<img src="https://example.com/tracking-pixel.png" width="1" height="1" alt="">
<p>Open any <code>.eml</code> file to view it here.</p>
<p>Happy reading!<br><strong>The InLook viewer</strong></p>
</body></html>

